N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 202.6 - Duties and functions of the committee

State Regulations

It shall be the function of the committee to advise with
the commissioner on all matters having to do with the promotion, advertising, publicity, marketing research and informational services for sour cherries
under this order. Committee members shall serve during the commissioner's
pleasure. Notes
